('1003137', 'Givani Malik', 'ADAPTASI NOVEL PAYUNG BUTUT KANA NASKAH DRAMA "PAYUNG BUTUT" PIKEUN BAHAN PANGAJARAN APRESIASI DRAMA', 'Pendidikan Bahasa Daerah', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN BAHASA DAN SASTRA', 'Dr. Dedi Koswara, M.Hum.', 'Dr. Retty Isnendes, M.Hum.', 'Penelitian ini mendeskripsikan (1) struktur novel Payung Butut; (2) struktur cerita naskah drama "Payung Butut"; (3) transformasi antara novel dan naskah drama Payung Butut; dan (4) menerapkan hasil penelitian kedalam bahan pengajaran apresiasi di SMA. Untuk dapat menguraikan hal tersebut, maka dalam tulisan ini digunakan pendekatan strukturalisme, dengan metode deskriptif analitik. Untuk menganalisis data digunakan teknik analisis data dan teknik interpretasi. Hasilnya menunjukan (1) tema dalam novel ini adalah kesombongan akan garis keturunannya. Latar yang muncul adalah perkampungan; (2) tema naskah ini yaitu tentang kesombongan akan garis turunan dan persoalan cinta antara N?ng ?bah dan Suganda, menjadi tema turunan. latar tempat di perkampungan; (3) pada bentuk transformasi, terdapat beberapa struktur yang dimodifikasi yaitu tema, alur, latar, dan tokoh; (4) berdasarkan hasil penelitian in...', '2016', 'givgiv912@gmail.com'),
('1003146', 'Rani Widi Noortatik', 'Foreignization and Domestication Strategies in Cultural Words Translation of Dan Brown''s the Lost Sy', 'Bahasa dan Sastra Inggris', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN BAHASA DAN SASTRA', 'Drs. Ahsin Mohamad, M.Ag.', 'Susi Septaviana R., M.Pd.', 'This study seeks to analyze the categories of cultural words and the types of foreignization and domestication strategies in the cultural words translation of the novel entitled The Last Symbol written by Dan Brown. There are 118 cultural words taken as the data representative from the novel. The data were then analyzed qualitatively by using the theory of foreignization and domestication strategy continuum proposed by Pederson (2005) and the theory of cultural words categorization proposed by Newmark (1988). The findings shows that there are 5 categories of cultural words found from the data which are (1) ecology, (2) material culture, (3) gestures and habits, (4) organizations, customs, activities, procedures, concepts, and (5) social culture. Further, the findings also shows that the foreignization strategy is used to translate 76 (64,4%) cultural words from the data while domestication is u...', '2016', 'keirania@gmail.om'),
('1003156', 'Stefani Debora Amelia Gauland ', 'THE ANALYSIS OF TRANSLATION METHODS AND PROCEDURES IN THE ABSTRACTS OF SELECTED UNDERGRADUATE PAPERS', 'Pendidikan Bahasa Inggris', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN BAHASA DAN SASTRA', 'Prof. Dr. Nenden Sri Lengkanawati, M.Pd.', '', 'For completing the university level, all of the college students in Indonesia are required to write a scientific paper. The purpose of this paper is to enhance their capability in analysing some issues and to report it in a written research paper. Then for over-viewing the content of the undergraduate paper, they have to write an abstract. In a public university in Bandung, the abstract should be translated into one or more languages. The objectives of this research were to identify the translation methods and procedures mostly used in translating abstracts of undergraduate papers. The method used in the research is a descriptive qualitative method. The collected data showed that there were 77 sentences from eight selected abstracts with Literal Translation as the most translation method used (73%). The result also found that the translation procedures used in translating abstract of undergradu...', '2016', 'debora.stefani92@gmail.com'),
('1003172', 'Jenriko Sihotang', 'Pengaruh Model Teaching Games for Understanding (TGfU) Terhadap Keterampilan Bermain Futsal ', 'Pendidikan Guru Sekolah Dasar Pendidikan Jasmani', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN OLAHRAGA DAN KESEHATAN', 'Drs. Sucipto, M.Kes., AIFO.', 'Dr. Dian Budiana, M.Pd.', 'Telah dilakukan penelitian tentang "Pengaruh Model Teaching Games for Understanding (TGfU) Terhadap Keterampilan Bermain Futsal di SD KASIH BANGSA, Holis Bandung" Penelitian ini dilatarbelakangi oleh kurangnya penampilan bermain  siswa dalam permainan futsal. Adapun tujuan penelitian ini adalah untuk mengetahui apakah Model Teaching Games for Understanding (TGfU) berpengaruh terhadap keterampilan bermain Futsal siswa di SD KASIH BANGSA, Holis Bandung. Metode penelitian yang digunakan adalah  eksperimen dengan desain penelitian one group pretest-posttest design. Dalam penelitian ini sampel berjumlah 15 orang. Istrumen yang digunakan adalah GPAI ( Games Performance Assessment Instrument). Semua data dianalisis dengan menggunakan uji t. hasil pengujian data tersebut diperoleh angka thitung keterampilan bermain (1,944787008) lebih kecil dari ttabel (1.701) sehingga Ho ditolaak. Berdasarkan hasil pe...', '2016', 'rico.zhen@yahoo.co.id'),
('1003174', 'Ahmad Nurahman', 'Pengaruh Penggunaan Media Pembelajaran terhadap Motivasi Belajar Siswa Kelas XI IPS SMA Laboratorium', 'Pendidikan Akuntansi', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN EKONOMI DAN BISNIS', 'Drs. H. Faqih Samlawi, M.A.', '', 'Tujuan penelitian utk mengetahui gambaran penggunaan media pembelajaran dan motivasi belajar siswa, kls XI IPS SMA Laboratorium (Percontohan) UPI.Penelitian juga utk mengetahui pengaruh penggunaan media pembelajaran terhadap motivasi belajar siswa,kls XI IPS SMA Laboratorium (Percontohan) UPI. Penelitian menggunakan metode survey.Populasi yaitu siswa kls XI IPS 117 siswa. Sampel 30 orang siswa.Teknik pengambilan sampel Nonprobability Sampling, jenis Purposive. Data yg diambil tentang penggunaan media pembelajaran dan motivasi belajar, didapatkan dengan penyebaran angket. Perhitungan statistika dengan software SPSS v.16 for Windows.Gambaran penggunaan media pembelajaran pada kategori cukup baik,sebesar 59,50%. Motivasi belajar siswa pada kategori cukup baik sebesar 62,48%. Hasil penelitian penggunaan media pembelajaran berpengaruh terhadap motivasi belajar siswa, pada mata pelajaran akuntansi. H...', '2016', 'kilimiticksman@yahoo.co.id'),
('1003232', 'Seruni Gita Arantxa', 'An Analysis of Turn-Taking Patterns in English Classrooms in A Junior High School in Bandung', 'Bahasa dan Sastra Inggris', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN BAHASA DAN SASTRA', 'Eri Kurniawan, S.Pd., M.A., Ph.D.', '', 'The present study seeks to investigate turn-taking patterns among teacher-students in English classroom interactions. Data were taken from 60 students from two classes and a teacher. Each class consists of 30 students whose age ranges from 11 to 12 years old. Data were analyzed qualitatively and supported by descriptive quantification and based on turn taking theories proposed by Sacks et al. (1974).The findings show that there are three patterns which occur in English classroom interactions namely Self-Selects (SS), Current Speaker Selects The Next Speaker (CS2TNS), and Current Speaker Continuous (CSC). Moreover, the most frequent turn-taking pattern is Self-Selects which is dominantly used by the male students. It is in line with Swann (1992) who proposed that gender becomes one of factors in turn taking pattern where male students are more outspoken than female students in classroom interact...', '2016', 'arantxagita@gmail.com'),
('1003236', 'Mohammad Rizal Firdaus', 'Pengaruh Produk Wisata Terhadap Kepuasan Wisatawan di Wana Wisata Puncak Bintang Kabupaten Bandung', 'Manajemen Resort dan Leisure', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN ILMU PENGETAHUAN SOSIAL', 'Prof. Dr. Darsiharjo, MS.', 'Fitri Rahmafitria, M.Si.', '', '2016', 'bozal45@gmail.com'),
