('1005876', 'Imam', 'Alienation In Murakami''s Blind Willow Sleeping Woman', 'Bahasa dan Sastra Inggris', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN BAHASA DAN SASTRA', 'Dr. Rd. Safrina, M.A.', '', 'This study explores the aspects of alienation in three selected short stories from Blind Willow, Sleeping Woman: "A Folklore for My Generation: A Pre-History of Late-Stage Capitalism," "Tony Takitani," and "Firefly," and how these aspects manifest in the lives of the people in the selected stories. The study was conducted under postmodernist approach and employs Seeman''s Alienation Aspects (1959) as the theoretical framework of the study. The findings divulge that there are four alienation aspects palpable in the selected short stories: powerlessness, meaninglessness, normlessness, and social isolation. The alienation aspects found manifest through four key points i.e. the unknown origins of alienation, the problem of choices overload, the fragmentation of life aspects, and disconnected relational self. In postmodern perspective, Murakami''s Blind Willow, Sleeping Woman can be interpreted as a r...', '2016', 'imamimam911@gmail.com'),
('1005880', 'Galih Eka Putra', 'The Use of Cohesive Devices in English Education Students'' Writing', 'Pendidikan Bahasa Inggris', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN BAHASA DAN SASTRA', 'Prof. Fuad Abdul Hamied, M.A., Ph.D.', 'Rd. Della Nuridah Kartika Sari A., S.Pd., M.Ed.', 'This study discovers how cohesive devices used in twelve students'' writing written by four students - two high achiever learners and two low achiever learners - of English Education Program in Indonesian University. With the characteristics of case study approach, the research study applies a qualitative method research design and employs Halliday and Hasan''s (1976) taxonomy of cohesion framework as a ground theory and a tool for text analysis. The findings show that grammatical cohesive devices are used slightly more frequent than the lexical ones. The students frequently used reiteration followed by reference, conjunction, collocation, substitution, and ellipsis with two general functions; to remind the readers about the topic discussed and to show the position of the author within the text. Furthermore, it is realized that to some extent, the way students use cohesive devices is a little bit...', '2016', 'ekaputragalih@gmail.com'),
('1005907', 'Aida Fitriani', 'PENGARUH PENGGUNAAN ALAT BANTU PAPAN TOKTAK DAN BOLA KARET DALAM PEMBELAJARAN PERMAINAN BOLA VOLI TE', 'Pendidikan Jasmani, Kesehatan, dan Rekreasi', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN OLAHRAGA DAN KESEHATAN', 'Drs. Agus Mahendra, M.A.', 'Sufyar Mudjianto, M.Pd.', 'Penelitian ini dilatarbelakangi oleh rendahnya kemampuan siswa dalam pembelajaran permainan bola voli dimana terdapat kecenderungan siswa-siswi tidak mengikuti pembelajaran permainan bola voli karena merasa sakit ketika menggunakan bola standar, serta tidak adanya alat bantu pembelajaran yang digunakan. Untuk meningkatkan hasil belajar permainan bola voli, penulis mencoba menggunakan alat bantu papan toktak dan bola karet yang dirangkai dalam pendekatan volleyball like games. Metode penelitian ini adalah eksperimen. Instrumen penelitian yang digunakan adalah tes keterampilan bermain bola voli GPAI. Hipotesis dalam penelitian ini adalah terdapat pengaruh yang signifikan terhadap hasil belajar dari penggunaan alat bantu papan toktak dan bola karet dalam pembelajaran permainan bola voli. Hasil pengolahan data dan pengujian hipotesis menunjukan peningkatan hasil belajar permainan bola voli siswa SM...', '2016', 'pradaraditewibowo@gmail.com'),
