('1104741', 'Helmi Hindasah', 'TEACHER''S TREATMENT OF GENDER ISSUES PRESENTED IN TEXTBOOK TEXTS', 'Pendidikan Bahasa Inggris', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN BAHASA DAN SASTRA', 'Prof. Dr. Didi Suherdi, M.Ed.', 'Nicke Yunita Moecharam. S.Pd., M.A.', 'Most research under the topic of gender and foreign language textbooks have been focused solely on texts while the exploration of teacher''s treatment of it which cannot be predicted. It is aimed at investigating the ways in which the teacher treats gender issues presented in the textbook texts as learning materials and explored the topic of gender in relation to classroom interaction. It utilizes qualitative descriptive case study focusing on lessons in which the textbook presented some aspects of gender. The data shows that the texts used are considered as texts which maintain traditional representation of gender roles where the teacher mostly endorses the idea. It also revealed that the teacher ignores the discussion of possible gender issues and his treatment was somewhat unclear. From a FPDA perspective, competing discourses of gender differentiation and collaborative talk, actually work th...', '2016', 'helmihinda@gmail.com'),
